EXTRACTED VALUE: I didn't purchase this from Newegg this time, but I decided to write my review here since I write a lot of reviews here anyways
The video looked just like the pictures, grainy, out of focus, serious let down for sure.
Being that it does exactly what i need it to do. Take pics and vids on the fly.
Camera came with all accessories in like new condition.
Make sure you have an extra SD card! I got addicted to the burst setting(s) at first and ended up filling up my 4gb card really fast!
I would not hesitate to recommend this camera to you or anyone else.
I bought a 4GB SDHC class 6 card.
Can't wait to give a try to the video recording features !!
I have bought these for my 4 and 6 year old grandkids ( The canon A 480s) and have had no trouble for a year now.
newegg.com has my business from now on! I ordered it on the weekend and it arrived Thursday by UPS - just as promised by Newegg!
The biggest issues are the poor focus ability and especially the grainy, noisy pictures.
Newegg is an excellent company to buy from. Excellent prices and quick shipping!
Dont be memory card stingy and set picture quality to its highest, you can't replace original lost data from compression.
Don't be fooled by the complex nature it is genuinely easy to use in any mode.
The change to "MOV" format for movies was a poor decision. Canon should restore the AVI or Mpeg format.
HOWEVER, Newegg BLEW IT on this one. The combo newegg offers with the memory stick is useless. Just FYI.
Read some professional revies on this thing, you will be impressed. And check youtube for some video reviews too.
